A list of Honorary Guest Lecturers from the past few years:  2018, Ronald D. Fricker, Ph.D., Professor and Department Head, Department of Statistics, Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University.
 2016, Karen Khafadar, Ph.D., Commonwealth Professor and Chair, Department of Statistics, University of Virginia. Title: &ldquo;Detecting tiny signals in massive data from high-energy physics.&rdquo;&rdquo;
 Abstract: Experiments in high-energy physics provide terabytes of data, from which critical information about the state of matter, governed by the theory outlined in the &ldquo;Standard Model&rdquo;, must be extracted.
